Pick up towel hanging on wall.
Turn right, go to end of counter past sink.  Turn left to face counter area.
Place towel on back of towel, directly to the right of the other towel.

Walk back over to the back of the toilet.
Put the towel down on the back of the toilet to the right of the first one.
